# IBAN validation (ibanapi.com) — used by the /api/iban route to auto-fill
# BIC and bank name from a Beneficiary IBAN.
# Get a free key at https://www.ibanapi.com/.
# Locally: copy this file to .env.local and put your key there (never here).
# On Render/Vercel: add IBANAPI_KEY in the service's Environment settings.
# Leave this example value blank — .env.example IS committed to git.
IBANAPI_KEY=

# Optional: override the upstream endpoint (defaults to ibanapi.com v1 validate).
# IBANAPI_URL=https://api.ibanapi.com/v1/validate
